BestSoFar.framework.core.helper

Class History

  • java.lang.Object
    • BestSoFar.framework.core.helper.History
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HistoryImpl

    public abstract class History
extends Object
    Each History object represents a unique sequence of Processor objects - ie. no two histories share the same sequence of Processor objects (without being the same object).

    Each History object contains a reference to the History object that came immediately before it, and a list of references to the History objects which have come after it.

    Each history begins with the same epoch (which is a singleton). To create a new history:

    History newHistory = History.getEpoch().createNext(creator);
